    "content": "This example application demonstrates how to use the SERCOM peripheral in slave mode. ",
    "url": "http://localhost:4000/csp_apps_pic32cm_le_ls/apps/sercom/i2c/slave/i2c_eeprom_emulation/readme.html#sercom-i2c-eeprom-emulation-i2c-slave",
